name: PASSWORD RESET - As a user who forgot my password, I want to reset my password so that I can regain access to my account

steps.name: User is in to the BlazeDemo reset password page
User enters a registered email
User clicks on Send Password Reset Link button
User should be redirected to a confirmation page indicating that a password reset link has been sent to their email
